<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4692112>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 2. Tagalis graziae sp. nov., male genitalia. A-C. Pygophore, left paramere removed; A. lateral view; B. dorsal view; C. caudal view; D. paramere; E-G. phallus; E. lateral view; F. ventral view; G. dorsal view. Abbreviations: ao, anterior opening of pygophore; apt, arms of articulatory apparatus; br, transverse bridge of pygophore; ese, endosomal sclerites; dps, dorsal phallotecal sclerite; go, genital opening of pygophore; mpp, posteromedial process of pygophore; pgo, process of genital opening; ps, paramere socket; pro, dorsal phallothecal sclerite prolongation." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4692112/files/figure.png" .

